en: The Harrington Education Center Office Tower was built in 1973 and the Harrington Education Center Classroom Building in 1974. Named for Marion T. Harrington, class of 1922. Harrington was a former president of Texas A&M (1950-53 and 1957-59) and first chancellor of the Texas A&M System (1953-65).
